theorem Topology.closure_interior_iter_six_eq
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure
        (interior
          (closure
            (interior
              (closure
                (interior
                  (closure
                    (interior
                      (closure
                        (interior
                          (A : Set X))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  -- Simplify the innermost fivefold iteration using the existing lemma.
  have h :=
    Topology.closure_interior_iter_five_eq (X := X) (A := A)
  -- Finish by applying the idempotence lemma once more.
  simpa [h] using
    (Topology.closure_interior_closure_interior_eq (X := X) (A := A))

theorem Topology.isOpen_of_isClosed_and_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (h_closed : IsClosed (A : Set X)) (hP3 : Topology.P3 (X := X) A) :
    IsOpen (A : Set X) := by
  exact
    (Topology.P3_iff_isOpen_of_isClosed (X := X) (A := A) h_closed).1 hP3
